  "texts": [
    "AI has a lot to offer in terms of time savings for lesson planning and resource preparation.",
    "Here are some instances of how ChatGPT can help you finish lesson planning and resource preparation faster: quick question generation, gap-fill activities, design math and science word problems, writing examples, writing feedback, personalization and differentiation, discussion prompts, one-on-one tutoring or coaching, and letters and communications [16][17][18][19][20].On the other hand, there are some disadvantages.",
    "(i) Materials produced by AI might be prejudiced or contain inaccuracies, particularly if they are not thoroughly evaluated by humans before usage.",
    "(ii) Lessons that are overly reliant on the instrument are likely to be highly standardized.",
    "Planning and preparing for the learning demands in our classrooms is still of utmost importance."
  ],
